.89081 5.59159 3.52705V3.90784H2.64768V3.52701ZM1.07764 3.98612V3.5271C1.07761 2.9035 1.13303 2.02667 1.57472 1.29344C2.06358 0.481912 2.9234 0 4.17848 0C4.7856 0 5.31228 0.108387 5.75387 0.339132C6.20431 0.574499 6.52343 0.915123 6.73854 1.30469C7.14266 2.03656 7.16164 2.92081 7.16164 3.52705V3.98612C7.75491 4.18614 8.18213 4.7471 8.18213 5.40784V8.50003C8.18213 9.32845 7.51056 10 6.68213 10H1.55713C0.728702 10 0.0571289 9.32845 0.0571289 8.50003V5.40785C0.0571289 4.7471 0.484353 4.18613 1.07764 3.98612Z\" fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></div></button><span id=\":Rtlgsmh:\" style=\"position:fixed\"></span></div></div></div><div class=\"aB40zqNSml1nCbUuOh7V\" data-type=\"pronunciation-toggle\"><p>[ <!-- -->ak-<strong>tiv</strong>-i-tee<!-- --> ]</p><fieldset><label><input type=\"radio\" checked=\"\" value=\"phonetic\"/><span>Phonetic (Standard)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" value=\"ipa\"/><span>IPA</span></label></fieldset></div></section></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section class=\"uLEIc6UAEiaBDDj6qSnO\" data-type=\"part-of-speech-module\"><div><div class=\"S3nX0leWTGgcyInfTEbW\" id=\"american-activity-noun\"><h2>noun</h2><div class=\"y0ZrXkbLi0mW1fbFOOIa\">, <i><em>plural </em><strong>ac·tiv·i·ties.</strong></i></div></div><ol class=\"lpwbZIOD86qFKLHJ2ZfQ E53FcpmOYsLLXxtj5omt\" data-type=\"definition-content-list\"><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->the state or quality of being active:</div></div><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><p><i>There was not much activity in the stock market today. He doesn&#x27;t have enough physical activity in his life.</i></p></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->a specific deed, action, function, or sphere of action:</div></div><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><p><i>social activities.</i></p></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->work, especially in elementary grades at school, that involves direct experience by the student rather than textbook study.</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->energetic activity; animation; liveliness.</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->a use of energy or force; an active movement or operation.</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->normal mental or bodily power, function, or process.</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <em>Physical Chemistry. </em>the capacity of a substance to react, corrected for the loss of reactivity due to the interaction of its constituents.</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <em>Physics. </em></div></div><ol class=\"JEKAKEmQ7ArHPGGbEHB2\"><li><div>the number of atoms of a radioactive substance that disintegrate per unit of time, usually expressed in curies.</div></li><li><div><a href=\"/browse/radioactivity\">radioactivity</a>.</div></li></ol></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->an organizational unit or the function it performs.</div></div></span></li></ol><div class=\"pzAb4KG141SuMsit5NFK\"><hr/><div></div><hr/></div></div></section></div></div></section><section class=\"LOhivfok408KJsgcv8Ab\" data-type=\"british-dictionary-entries-module\"><div class=\"\"><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section class=\"RU3P4mEiPC1uju7Hv6Yw\" data-type=\"dictionary-headword-module\"><div class=\"bZjAAKVoBi7vttR0xUts\"><p class=\"elMfuCTjKMwxtSEEnUsi\">activity</p><div class=\"AooatC8noO9cmWd95rMo\"><div data-type=\"favorite-star-button\"><button class=\"QTJM4SbhRNoVJ0mJxTKC\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"definition\" data-linkname=\"favorited:activity\" data-linktype=\"favorited\"><svg class=\"hKc5_7ESpepHS_34gUUw\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" width=\"32\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M480 208H308L256 48l-52 160H32l140 96-54 160 138-100 138 100-54-160z\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"32\"></path></svg><div class=\"cqzC99lPmU5QagY9EdW7\"><svg class=\"hKc5_7ESpepHS_34gUUw\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 9 10\" width=\"9\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><script type=\"text/comment\"><!--! Font Awesome Pro 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. --></script><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M2.64768 3.52701C2.64765 2.94821 2.71391 2.46229 2.91203 2.13341C3.06298 1.88282 3.3611 1.60321 4.17848 1.60321C4.60759 1.60321 4.8738 1.68019 5.03865 1.76633C5.19465 1.84785 5.29554 1.95562 5.37091 2.0921C5.54773 2.41233 5.59159 2.89081 5.59159 3.52705V3.90784H2.64768V3.52701ZM1.07764 3.98612V3.5271C1.07761 2.9035 1.13303 2.02667 1.57472 1.29344C2.06358 0.481912 2.9234 0 4.17848 0C4.7856 0 5.31228 0.108387 5.75387 0.339132C6.20431 0.574499 6.52343 0.915123 6.73854 1.30469C7.14266 2.03656 7.16164 2.92081 7.16164 3.52705V3.98612C7.75491 4.18614 8.18213 4.7471 8.18213 5.40784V8.50003C8.18213 9.32845 7.51056 10 6.68213 10H1.55713C0.728702 10 0.0571289 9.32845 0.0571289 8.50003V5.40785C0.0571289 4.7471 0.484353 4.18613 1.07764 3.98612Z\" fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></div></button><span id=\":Rtlh4mh:\" style=\"position:fixed\"></span></div></div></div><div class=\"aB40zqNSml1nCbUuOh7V\" data-type=\"pronunciation-toggle\"><p>/ <!-- -->ækˈtɪvɪtɪ<!-- --> /</p></div></section><section class=\"uLEIc6UAEiaBDDj6qSnO\" data-type=\"part-of-speech-module\"><div><div class=\"S3nX0leWTGgcyInfTEbW\" id=\"british-activity-noun\"><h2>noun</h2></div><ol class=\"lpwbZIOD86qFKLHJ2ZfQ E53FcpmOYsLLXxtj5omt\" data-type=\"definition-content-list\"><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->the state or quality of being active</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->lively action or movement</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->any specific deed, action, pursuit, etc</div></div><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><p><i>recreational activities</i></p></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> <!-- -->the number of disintegrations of a radioactive substance in a given unit of time, usually expressed in curies or disintegrations per second</div></div></span></li><li><span class=\"HGU9YJqWX_GVHkeeJhSH\"><div class=\"NZKOFkdkcvYgD3lqOIJw\"><div> </div></div><ol class=\"JEKAKEmQ7ArHPGGbEHB2\"><li><div>the capacity of a substance to undergo chemical change</div></li><li><div>the effective concentration of a substance in a chemical system. The <strong>absolute activity<!-- --> </strong>of a substance B, λ <!-- -->B <!-- -->, is defined as exp (μ <!-- -->B <em>RT </em>) where μ <!-- -->B <!-- -->is the chemical potential</div></li></ol></span></li></ol><div class=\"pzAb4KG141SuMsit5NFK\"><hr/><div></div><hr/></div></div></section></div></div></section><div data-wknd-infeed-div=\"true\"></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section class=\"ZScNxuAtfMdhoCsqbzGi\" data-type=\"other-words-from\"><h2 class=\"KhyRmcN6T1mkCS6cmpkT hFymlk9KE06_fSxWotl3\" id=\"other-words-from\">Discover More</h2><h2 class=\"hjIscPSvedrZbuT26ZYc\">Other Words From</h2><ul><li><strong>non·ac·tiv·i·ty<!-- --> </strong>noun <em>plural </em><strong>nonactivities</strong></li><li><strong>pre·ac·tiv·i·ty<!-- --> </strong>noun <em>plural </em><strong>preactivities</strong></li><li><strong>su·per·ac·tiv·i·ty<!-- --> </strong>noun <em>plural </em><strong>superactivities</strong></li></ul></section></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section class=\"bLQY4HuOoBYj7mHuUnvO\" data-type=\"origins-module\"><h2 class=\"KhyRmcN6T1mkCS6cmpkT v64dancTwzffhlHDy4y0\" id=\"word-history-and-origins\">Discover More</h2><h2>Word History and Origins</h2><div class=\"yX4FEAQxKpoMaTLO2pCw\"><p>Origin of<!-- --> <a class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" href=\"/browse/activity\">activity<sup>1</sup></a></p><div>First recorded in <!-- -->1520–30; <!-- -->from <em>Middle French </em>or directly from <em>Medieval Latin </em><em>āctīvitās; </em><a href=\"/browse/active\">active</a>,<!-- --> <a href=\"/browse/ity\">-ity</a></div></div></section></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section data-type=\"example-sentences-module\"><h2 class=\"KhyRmcN6T1mkCS6cmpkT BsLEokjNzgvQY0xyORKn\" id=\"example-sentences\">Discover More</h2><h2 class=\"tEJceV7YF9MUrC51KXg7\">Example Sentences</h2><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>What I discovered about sunflower seeds then, and continue to love about them now, is that, as with many worthwhile things, they are about the process, as much an activity as a food.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"https://www.eater.com/21438671/david-sunflower-seeds-is-an-ideal-snack-for-restlessness-and-anxiety\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Eater\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"https://www.eater.com/21438671/david-sunflower-seeds-is-an-ideal-snack-for-restlessness-and-anxiety\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eater</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>This helped confirm economic activity in the third-quarter has greatly surprised to the upside.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/17/global-stocks-tumble-powell-fed-interest-rates/\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Fortune\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/17/global-stocks-tumble-powell-fed-interest-rates/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fortune</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>For participating in activities like swimming and yoga and completing health screenings and immunizations, users can earn a maximum of around $280 over the program’s two-year run.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/16/apple-watch-exercise-work-out-singapore-pay-government/\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Fortune\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/16/apple-watch-exercise-work-out-singapore-pay-government/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fortune</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>Noonan said his wife, a hairstylist, monitors the online activity of their daughters more closely than he does, and that their work is often a topic of conversation when the family convenes in the evening.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/turning-point-teens-disinformation-trump/2020/09/15/c84091ae-f20a-11ea-b796-2dd09962649c_story.html\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Washington Post\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/turning-point-teens-disinformation-trump/2020/09/15/c84091ae-f20a-11ea-b796-2dd09962649c_story.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Washington Post</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>He has also resisted changing the computer models, they said, including adding new types of data that’s standard at other firms such as tracking oil tankers and credit card activity.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/15/the-losses-continue-to-pile-up-for-hedge-fund-king-ray-dalio/\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Fortune\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/15/the-losses-continue-to-pile-up-for-hedge-fund-king-ray-dalio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fortune</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>The most recent activity had a high point of 3.6 on the Richter Scale.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/07/26-earthquakes-later-fracking-s-smoking-gun-is-in-texas.html?source=dictionary\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:The Daily Beast\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/07/26-earthquakes-later-fracking-s-smoking-gun-is-in-texas.html?source=dictionary\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Daily Beast</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>“There is nothing whatsoever in the video which supports the charges—it shows no criminal activity,” Bakir said.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/30/sisi-is-persecuting-prosecuting-and-publicly-shaming-egypt-s-gays.html?source=dictionary\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:The Daily Beast\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/30/sisi-is-persecuting-prosecuting-and-publicly-shaming-egypt-s-gays.html?source=dictionary\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Daily Beast</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>The masterpiece is huge, but structurally flawed and terribly vulnerable to seismic activity.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/25/florence-preps-david-for-the-big-one.html?source=dictionary\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:The Daily Beast\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/25/florence-preps-david-for-the-big-one.html?source=dictionary\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Daily Beast</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>Moreover, trucks, dust, and boomtown stress are the effects of any large-scale industrial activity.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/20/new-york-s-conservative-fracking-ban.html?source=dictionary\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:The Daily Beast\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/20/new-york-s-conservative-fracking-ban.html?source=dictionary\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Daily Beast</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>Some of them, including Kurnosova, escaped the country as they faced a possible jail term for their opposition activity.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/16/russians-exiles-organizing-to-oust-putin.html?source=dictionary\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:The Daily Beast\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/12/16/russians-exiles-organizing-to-oust-putin.html?source=dictionary\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Daily Beast</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>Other factors being equal, the amount of urea indicates the activity of metabolism.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/47078/47078-h/47078-h.htm\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Project Gutenberg\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/47078/47078-h/47078-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Gutenberg</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>In disease, the amount of solids depends mainly upon the activity of metabolism and the ability of the kidneys to excrete.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/47078/47078-h/47078-h.htm\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Project Gutenberg\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/47078/47078-h/47078-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Gutenberg</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>No young Cave Swallows were taken and gonads of adults were in various stages of reproductive activity.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/36473/36473-h/36473-h.htm\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Project Gutenberg\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/36473/36473-h/36473-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Gutenberg</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>It is the will directing the activity of the intellect into some particular channel and keeping it there.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/25354/25354-h/25354-h.htm\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Project Gutenberg\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/25354/25354-h/25354-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Gutenberg</a></div></div><div class=\"dkA1ih27tI9o0MHLDxKt\"><p>Both animal and man seemed to be dozing, but they woke into activity when the sahib approached.</p><div>From<!-- --> <a href=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/36478/36478-h/36478-h.htm\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\" data-analytics=\"aa-track\" data-linklocation=\"body\" data-linkmodule=\"example-sentences-module\" data-linkname=\"from:Project Gutenberg\" data-linktype=\"link\" data-linkurl=\"http://www.gutenberg.org/files/36478/36478-h/36478-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Gutenberg</a></div></div></section></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE eK0SbwCbuTiZNmg5Q8ag\"><div class=\"SZjJlj7dd7R6mDTODwIT\"><p class=\"ZBaOeEicp1FaXQoUFZBy\">Advertisement</p><div class=\"dictionary_content_300x250_noflex_1\"></div></div></div><div class=\"YommMxopETPCP_wzxPxE\"><section class=\"b4webt3xsd_nEZu_TYgF\" data-type=\"dictionary-related-words-module\"><h2 class=\"KhyRmcN6T1mkCS6cmpkT USrI433LPq9JKfoEJgMw\" id=\"related-words\">Discover More</h2><h2 class=\"SeO7_NoJrJTocIik6N74\">Related Words</h2><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/act\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">act</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/endeavor\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">endeavor</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/enterprise\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">enterprise</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/job\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">job</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/project\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">project</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/scheme\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">scheme</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/task\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">task</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/venture\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">venture</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com:80/browse/work\" class=\"TSqnrw0qSMGseOGGBuxc\">work</a></li></ul></section></div><div class=\"YommMxop